{"title":"Leetcode","uid":"a149f98784797549d63d0fc2a0472ac5","slug":"C/Leetcode","date":"2022-06-01T03:39:04.000Z","updated":"2022-06-16T09:31:36.904Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/C/Leetcode.json","keywords":null,"cover":"/img/C.jpeg","content":"<h2 id=\"排序\"><a href=\"#排序\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"排序\"></a>排序</h2><h3 id=\"自定义排序\"><a href=\"#自定义排序\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"自定义排序\"></a>自定义排序</h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">sort(array.begin(), array.end(), \n    [](vector&lt;int&gt;&amp; a, vector&lt;int&gt;&amp; b)&#123;return a[0]&lt;b[0] || a[0]&#x3D;&#x3D;b[0]&amp;&amp;a[1]&gt;b[1];&#125;\n);<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<h3 id=\"快排”枢轴”思想\"><a href=\"#快排”枢轴”思想\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"快排”枢轴”思想\"></a>快排”枢轴”思想</h3><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>找第key小的元素，每次舍去枢轴另一侧，复杂度logn</p></blockquote>\n<details class=\"custom-details\">\n<summary>Click to see more</summary>\n<p><pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">int key;\nvoid Qsort(int a[], int l ,int r)&#123;\n  while(l&lt;&#x3D;r)&#123;\n    int pivot &#x3D; Part(a,l,r);\n    if(pivot&#x3D;&#x3D;key) do();\n    else if(pivot&gt;key) r&#x3D;pivot-1;\n    else l&#x3D;pivot+1;\n  &#125;\n&#125;\nint Part(int a[], int l, int r)&#123;\n  int pivot &#x3D; a[l];\n  while(l&lt;r)&#123;\n    while(l&lt;r &amp;&amp; a[r]&gt;&#x3D;pivot) r--;\n    a[l]&#x3D;a[h];\n    while(l&lt;r &amp;&amp; a[l]&lt;&#x3D;pivot) l++;\n    a[h]&#x3D;a[l];\n  &#125;\n  a[l] &#x3D; pivot;\n  return l;\n&#125;<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n</p>\n</details>\n<h3 id=\"优先队列-前k大问题\"><a href=\"#优先队列-前k大问题\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"优先队列(前k大问题)\"></a>优先队列(前k大问题)</h3><h2 id=\"双指针\"><a href=\"#双指针\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"双指针\"></a>双指针</h2><h3 id=\"142-环形链表-II\"><a href=\"#142-环形链表-II\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"142. 环形链表 II\"></a><a href=\"https://leetcode.cn/problems/linked-list-cycle-ii/\">142. 环形链表 II</a></h3><p>题目：输入一个链表，输出环的入节点，否则返回空指针</p>\n<p>题解：链表找环路——<strong>快慢指针（Floyed判圈法）</strong>。从head开始，指针fast和slow每次前进2、1步，若无环则能走到尽头，否则两者会相遇。第一次相遇时，令fast=head，此后fast和slow每次均前进一步，第二次相遇时节点即为入环节点。</p>\n<details class=\"custom-details\">\n<summary>Click to see more</summary>\n<p><pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">ListNode *detectCycle(ListNode* head)&#123;\n    ListNode *slow&#x3D;head,*head&#x3D;head;\n    do&#123;\n        if(!fast || !fast-&gt;next) return nullptr;\n        fast &#x3D; fast-&gt;next-&gt;next;\n        slow &#x3D; slow-&gt;next;\n    &#125;while(fast !&#x3D; slow);\n    fast &#x3D; head;\n    while(fast !&#x3D; slow)&#123;\n        slow &#x3D; slow-&gt;next;\n        fast &#x3D; fast-&gt;next;\n    &#125;\n    return fast;\n&#125;<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n</p>\n</details>\n<h2 id=\"二分法\"><a href=\"#二分法\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"二分法\"></a>二分法</h2><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p><a href=\"https://leetcode.cn/circle/article/xYBtLt/\">二分法题单</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://leetcode.cn/link/?target=https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1d54y1q7k7\">B站视频</a></p></blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"蓝红二分法\"><a href=\"#蓝红二分法\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"蓝红二分法\"></a>蓝红二分法</h3><p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Yveltals/Picgo/%E8%93%9D%E7%BA%A2%E4%BA%8C%E5%88%86%E6%B3%95.png\"></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">l&#x3D;-1, r&#x3D;n;\nwhile(l+1&lt;r)&#123;\n    int m&#x3D;(l+r)&gt;&gt;1; &#x2F;&#x2F; m∈[0,n-1]\n    if(isBlue(m)) l&#x3D;m;\n    else r&#x3D;m;\n&#125;\nreturn l&#x2F;r; &#x2F;&#x2F;lr是蓝红分界线<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<h3 id=\"lower-bound函数\"><a href=\"#lower-bound函数\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"lower_bound函数\"></a>lower_bound函数</h3><p>返回首个<code>≥x</code>的迭代器</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">int *p &#x3D; lower_bound(a.begin(),a.end(),x)<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p>返回首个<code>&gt;x</code>的迭代器</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">int *p &#x3D; upper_bound(a.begin(),a.end(),x)<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n","feature":true,"text":"排序自定义排序sort(array.begin(), array.end(), [](vector&lt;int&gt;&amp; a, vector&lt;int&gt;&amp; b)&#123;return a[0]&lt;b[0] || a[0]&#x3D;&#x3D;b...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1.7k","symbolsTime":"2 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"C","slug":"C","count":3,"path":"api/categories/C.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"C","slug":"C","count":3,"path":"api/tags/C.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%8E%92%E5%BA%8F\"><span class=\"toc-text\">排序</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E8%87%AA%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89%E6%8E%92%E5%BA%8F\"><span class=\"toc-text\">自定义排序</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%BF%AB%E6%8E%92%E2%80%9D%E6%9E%A2%E8%BD%B4%E2%80%9D%E6%80%9D%E6%83%B3\"><span class=\"toc-text\">快排”枢轴”思想</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%BC%98%E5%85%88%E9%98%9F%E5%88%97-%E5%89%8Dk%E5%A4%A7%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98\"><span class=\"toc-text\">优先队列(前k大问题)</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%8F%8C%E6%8C%87%E9%92%88\"><span class=\"toc-text\">双指针</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#142-%E7%8E%AF%E5%BD%A2%E9%93%BE%E8%A1%A8-II\"><span class=\"toc-text\">142. 环形链表 II</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%BA%8C%E5%88%86%E6%B3%